column12: Host Greg Fitzgerald; Amy Sands reports on women in Boston's black community learning how to defend themselves with firearms; Henrietta Davis visits project SCALE that fights adult illiteracy; David Freudberg learns about the MBTA (Part 4 of a series on the T); Shelly Roth speaks to an environmental lobbyist who fights for non-smokers' rights.
